{
  "stem": "27335.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was-- he was-- he was a locksmith, I take, or something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They came to visit on a bright June Sunday afternoon, came with this Leduc blacksmith-- he brought him out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, these are the new arrivals in our Hungarian community.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not-- not in Alberta.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one of them, the shoemaker brought a copy of the Canadian Hungarian [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yeah, so, in-- about three months in Canada, we already had-- I doubt they called it a communist paper, you see, but that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "See, it was narrated by communists in Toronto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was speaking our language.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was special-- my father, when he first read it, the first page, and he kissed it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, well, I'm right at home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh, no he never belonged to any organization in-- in-- Hun-- well, he--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, in Canada, I mean.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh-- oh, in Canada-- well, then, at that age-- at that age-- well, I was-- I was in the frontline, already, as far as the organization, and so on.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I-- I was the younger, and I-- I used to go [INAUDIBLE] on hiking, and so on, and so.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When that, we had an organization, a Hungarian organization, a leftist organization-- cultural, and [INAUDIBLE] organization, and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, uh, came a national organizer from-- from-- from Toronto-- he was on a-- on a tour in Western Canada-- and he heard about-- about this-- specially did this family, this harness-maker family, in Leduc, and he stopped.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so in 19-- it was in 1933-- and then he just grabbed me and took me into Edmonton, right into the office of the communist boss.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I'm not hiding my-- my past, and that's how it-- that's how it happened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
